kuantar dia pulang, jadi jangan khawatir.

93
00:10:03,999 --> 00:10:07,337
Apa kau harus sejauh ini?
Kenapa tingkahmu seperti anak kecil?

94
00:10:07,337 --> 00:10:09,274
Baguslah.

95
00:10:09,274 --> 00:10:11,149
Karena aku anak kecil,
dan kau orang dewasa...,

96
00:10:11,174 --> 00:10:12,798
...kau bisa melakukan
segalanya untukku.

97
00:10:24,506 --> 00:10:26,501
<i>Mustahil.</i>

98
00:10:37,599 --> 00:10:39,861
Sudah saatnya minum obat.

99
00:10:39,861 --> 00:10:42,135
Kenapa dia duduk seperti itu?

100
00:10:47,758 --> 00:10:49,551
Benarkah itu?

101
00:10:50,684 --> 00:10:54,714
Apa Ketua Nam benar-benar tahu tentang dia?

102
00:10:54,714 --> 00:10:58,671
Apa?/ Dia bilang kau kenal Ketua Nam.

103
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:01,999
Itu tak benar, 'kan?

104
00:11:02,580 --> 00:11:04,546
Soal itu...

105
00:11:06,927 --> 00:11:10,277
Jangan bilang.../
Akan kujelaskan semuanya.

106
